title: Ep 120 - Blind Serial Killers
description: The boys were on a roll today. Gumpy managed to get back in America, Todd is still battling his mice infestation, Digs talks about his bachelor party weekend, Nick gives us some TV and movie recommendations, and they all discuss how the world will end from a viral outbreak.
